<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.8.10">
<l>cīrmaikoḷ vīṭu cuvarkka narakīṟā</l>
<l>vīrmaiko ṭēvar naṭuvāmaṟ ṟepporuṭkum</l>
<l>vērmutalāy vittāy parantutaṉi niṉṟa</l>
<l>kārmukilpōl vaṇṇaṉeṉ kaṇṇaṉaināṉ kaṇṭēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have seen Kṛṣṇa, the one with a colour like rain clouds,</l>
<l>who stands alone, spreading, being famous liberation, heaven</l>
<l>[and] finally hell, being in the middle of the affectionate gods,</l>
<l>being the seed, being the root cause for everything else.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
